script_search_path(25.10)                            script_search_path(25.10)

Name
       script_search_path

Syntax
        script_search_path

       Default:  ".". The default value represents the current application run
       directory.

       Provides a set of directories for the software to search for files that
       are sourced using the Tcl source command. The  software  searches  each
       search path directory for the specified file.

